*******************************************************
Revolt of the Ultra-Contemporaries ( https://puck.news/the-revolt-of-the-ul=
tra-contemporaries/?utm_campaign=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%283%2F7%2F25%2=
9&utm_content=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%283%2F7%2F25%29&utm_medium=3Demai=
l_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a )
